HEADWORD: Other
<hw>Oth"er</hw> <pr>(⟦ucr⟧⟦th⟧"⟦etil⟧r)</pr>, <pos>adv.</pos>
<def>Otherwise.</def> ⟦ldquo⟧It shall none <xex>other</xex> be.⟦rdquo⟧
